Migration
---------
On first startup after this change, FactLedger.load() detects the old
EditLedger format (entries with "edit_id") and auto-migrates:
  - Each triple → QAPair (question derived from relation, value = object)
  - Junk entries filtered (category labels, placeholders, commentary)
  - Stages, training counts, degrade counts preserved
  - File overwritten with new format

The old memit.py is not imported by any active code path.
